<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF108-624-014  </DOCNO><DOCID>08 624 014.andO;</DOCID><JOURNAL>Computer Reseller News  July 2 1990 n375 p57(1).andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Turn on the 'light': SunRiver adds workstation. (SunRiverLightStation) (product announcement)andM;</TITLE><TEXT><ABSTRACT>SunRiver Corp's new LightStation is a workstation targeted at thecomputer-aided design (CAD) market.andP;  It can be connected to othercomputers through SunRiver's fiber-optic cabling.andP;  The machine isbased on Texas Instrument's 34010 and 34020 graphics processorsand offers multiuser, multitasking 32-bit graphics processing forAutoCAD and other CAD programs.andP;  The workstation is part of acomplete line of CAD products introduced by SunRiver in Mar, 1990.andO;The LightStation is currently shipping for a $3,499 list price.andP;  APC LightCard is available for $999 and a LightAdapter costs $699.andO;CADMagic software lists for $495.andM;</ABSTRACT></TEXT><DESCRIPT>Company:   SunRiver Corp. (product introduction).andO;Product:   SunRiver LightStation (Workstation) (product introduction).andO;Topic:     Computer-Aided DesignWorkstationsProduct Introduction.andM;</DESCRIPT></DOC>